Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是阿爾貝魯特王嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.72,0:00:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特魯夫  你這是打算幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必和我一起品嘗美味的西餐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  很遺憾  你的那份好像沒有預定的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它捆緊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目標果然是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來差不多也該結束和可愛公主的捉迷藏遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝魯特王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  阿爾貝魯特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去那邊看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  小的們  目標是「WOOD CUBE」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時先別把公主殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做這種事情  你認為我會原諒你嗎  特魯夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被原諒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會來對我下達審判？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經沒有你的人了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝魯特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所計劃的這次環球旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說是最佳時機哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為除了國王和公主以外的人都已經被我的部下所佔據
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼！  為什麼你要背叛我  特魯夫！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  說得真難聽啊  阿爾貝魯特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很感謝你喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將身為孤兒的我撫養至今  甚至連王國的指揮官都讓我來擔任呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我一點野心都沒有而輔佐你至今嗎？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是神對你的正當的制裁  阿爾貝魯特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特魯夫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到公主了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  馬上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  就是這樣  你也該想好遺言要說什麼了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝魯特王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個背叛者！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經分不清狀況了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是史黛拉公主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心情可好～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特魯夫  你這傢伙知道自己在做什麼嗎混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是老樣子  長著一副可愛的臉  說話卻很粗魯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道我在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把這塊阿爾貝魯特王的「WOOD CUBE」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和公主的「WOOD CUBE」一起入手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喚醒古代兵器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:04:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是為了讓我成為菲茵王國新的國王！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經沒有你的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經無法逃走了哦  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  老實地把那個交給我！…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特魯夫大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主～  好嘞～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主～  好嘞～ xN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這筆賬利息可是很高的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  帶我去父王那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  「WOOD CUBE」？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主應該有好好帶在身上的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！  等…  誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…不是能讓我成為國王的東西嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不不  等會兒  冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先理清下頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵生活12年以來  我一直認為我就會這樣直到死去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會遇到這種機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我成了國王也沒有任何想法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且拿到這兩塊東西之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道喚醒古代兵器的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  燙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO！！！！！！！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:15.86,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\Nの\N27
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:27.61,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,260)\fad(600,600)}彩\N票
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了  太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒  我買彩票中了10萬円哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  要請客喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎麼辦呢  要買什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要乾脆買套房呢  開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張是去年的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:08:02.44,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(650,250)\fad(600,600)}禮\N物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛  彩票這種東西本來就很難中啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就別安慰我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  今天不是祐子的生日嗎  給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  不會吧  禮物？  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以拆開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只是一點小意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是碰巧家裡有的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  你有這份心意我就很開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}章魚芥末
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  高崎老師  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:43.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}相生這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  你有沒有辦法治治相生這傢伙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她總是不寫作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你作為班主任這樣給她頭上來一發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會轉告給相生同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那麼我就去上第一堂課了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧  茶沒有灑出來吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.28,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(40,300)\fad(0,0)}日\N常\N之\N28
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想保護她啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於活了26年  完全沒有女人緣的我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井老師就像是庭院前突然冒出的竹筍般
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不可以不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為教育者把戀愛感情帶入職場中是荒謬至極的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點  高崎學！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記帶這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記帶這本黑色的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起  高崎老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的黑色本子是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高崎老師  你要把我的黑本子帶到哪裡去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那麼我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想邀請她去采香菇啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井老師現在有沒有男朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從她手上並沒有戴戒指可以推測她沒有結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底我有沒有機會呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的音樂是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的動物是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的運動是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的山菜是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我在想些什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心意不純啊心意不純  高崎學！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子的話怎麼能做學生的榜樣  幹出漂亮的工作呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高崎老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是在為學生的事情而煩惱著呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  只是問個喜歡的食物應該沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井老師喜歡的食物是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我什麼都吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香菇什麼的吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是烤還是煮都很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢  油炸也可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然！  油炸也OK！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油炸也可以呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要自然點  自然一點啊  高崎學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像跟家裡的茄子搭話一樣自然地說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是  什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  老是把你叫住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在有在交往的男朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了些什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋嗎  難道我是笨蛋嗎  還是傻子呢！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有男朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有哦…沒有哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長…長…長出來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  高崎老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉問了你這麼失禮的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果好就行！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井老師  第一堂課請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  高崎老師也要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  不好意思  我就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高崎老師也要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高崎老師也要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高崎老師也要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  那個…請把鐮刀還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把這把鐮刀賣掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買不到食物就會死翹翹的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  有條河
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把鐮刀還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後出布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂出喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我贏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是只有這麼點兒！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免費附送…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天之後的天氣是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡一投！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來才要動真格了的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我來試著說一件美緒腦中完全沒想過的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}「スチャラカ社員」馬馬虎虎社員，60年代播放的搞笑節目\Nスチャラカ是形容馬馬虎虎，吊兒郎當的樣子，現在用得不多了。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫篇「馬馬虎虎OL旅行日記」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:06.66,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(35,360)\fad(600,600)\fs30\bord15\shad0\be60\3a&H50\3c&HFFFFFF&}趕\N著\N跑\N進\N電\N車\N是\N很\N危\N險\N的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒  麻衣  電車就要開了  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  安全上壘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗噗  只有你一個人趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:24.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}印尼語再見的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Selamat Tinggal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:28.76,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,330)\fad(600,600)}要\N點\N什\N麼\N呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  請儘量點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金槍魚肚一份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鰤魚  不  幼鰤魚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請儘量點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我金槍魚和魚鰭肉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一份海膽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  金槍魚肚一份和…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我忘記了」喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.96,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N29
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  你…你好  有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等下  你從剛才開始就在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  因為很奇怪又有趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很普通的  發條只是裝飾品而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是怎麼做到的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴姐姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請還給我  請還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那麼就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:15:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉  開玩笑開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是玩笑呢  請還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你選哪邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我選包包！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  猜對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來第二問
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健太君的媽媽買了十個蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中三個被媽媽吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的其中的四個送給了鄰居由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答你的手腕在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在包包裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害  又是正確答案！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就快點還給我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是最後的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這個也答對了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能得到一個手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  那本來就是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想要手腕嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼提問
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把「包包」說十遍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:17:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包包…包包…包包…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫畫的時候 放在下面的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:06.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}包包「かばん」和畫板「がばん」諧音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是畫板啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正解是畫紙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣啊  太狡猾了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑哦  開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的   不要老是糾纏著我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  取下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取下來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  姐姐從大學回來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  剛才遇到了一個很有趣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手可以取下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有發條在的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有那樣的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:38.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,600)}一句話時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:44.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}因為括弧 「括弧（カッコ）」與 帥氣「格好いい（カッコいい）」諧音\N同時有想給「哦  真帥氣呢」這話加括弧的雙重含義…很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想成為「哦  真帥氣呢」這種感覺的型男呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:51.05,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,300)\fad(600,400)}日\N常\N之\N30
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  我要投嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔球～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  小鬼的程度就是這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩位是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全就沒有合上拍不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本  博士剛才得了幾分？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  博士我要投了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還沒有投啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要殺掉我嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生  我剛才得了幾分呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也這樣嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又揮棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  給你  阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我這雙手要怎麼拿球棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你以為我的手是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明肉球都被你們這麼隨便亂捏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你們這些小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  那個  因為就你們2個很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就看著你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會參加的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從投球接球開始練習怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  教練
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教練？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教練  手套只有一個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算空手接的話也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教練  我戴不好手套
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你不是戴在左手了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教練
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教練
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真拿你們沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  我要投了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管來！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  到哪兒去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:51.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}然後啊  我被老師罵了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:54.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哈哈  果然會這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:55.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}同感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:57.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}麻衣也那樣覺得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:21:00.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}但是也不用這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:03.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}也是吧  不過接下來要小心點才行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh  Gentleman
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:23.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是吧  雖然是那樣  麻衣要再借給我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:23.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:25.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊哈  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:28.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}果然人生就該有個朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姐姐說的那孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
